Matthias VogtVogt, 42, was previously general manager for finance at Afrox since July 2015 as part of the Afrox executive committee and played a key role in the company&#x2019;s 2015/2016 Swift turnaround ensuring Afrox derived the optimum benefits and successfully implements Shared Services for large parts of his function. Vogt attended University of Oxford SAID Business School and is a Graduate in Business & Administration (Audit, Tax and Controlling) of the Rosenheim University of Applied Sciences as Dipl.- Betriebswirt (FH).